sequenceDiagram
    participant WM as WorkModeMiddleware
    participant M as Model
    loop until no ready todos
        WM->>WM: pick first ready todo
        WM->>M: emit phase_started → "execute THIS step only"
        M-->>WM: step done
        WM->>WM: mark complete → emit phase_completed
    end
    WM->>M: all done → write final summary
    Note over WM: stuck? (pending but none ready)<br/>emit plan_adapted → ask user to revise
